00:01:04.820 --> 00:01:10.779
And the cool thing is that this TensorFlow eager execution, we can already do it in R

00:01:10.779 --> 00:01:16.260
since about last summer, so we've been preparing for it, so we're ready.

00:01:16.260 --> 00:01:21.500
And now in this talk, it's about like I want to show you why it's so cool that we can do

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:22.500
that.

