00:05:25.779 --> 00:05:32.220
And so these two are going to fight each other, and each is going to get better every time.

00:05:32.220 --> 00:05:37.980
Because as the discriminator gets better discerning between fake and real images, the generator

00:05:37.980 --> 00:05:40.260
is going to generate better images.

