of things conceptually.

00:06:34.559 --> 00:06:40.040
And there's one thing I need to introduce, which applies to eager execution as well as

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:41.559
static execution.

00:06:41.559 --> 00:06:50.320
We can have Keras custom models in our, let's say, since last summer, approximately.

