I think they perhaps even look better than the input.

00:09:20.919 --> 00:09:25.200
So it actually works.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:32.520
Similarly, if I use this other approach, the variation of the encoders, I don't have this

00:09:32.520 --> 00:09:39.239
antagonistic set-up of the generator and discriminator working against each other, but I still have

