an encoder and a decoder, so the encoder is trying to produce some latent code, and the

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:52.239
decoder is trying to reconstruct the input.

00:09:52.239 --> 00:09:54.640
And the set-up is pretty similar.

00:09:54.640 --> 00:09:56.119
You will see.

00:09:56.119 --> 00:10:03.000
So in this case, I was thinking I've generated these penguins, and so I want to generate

